# Supabase / Postgres

## Rules

- **Migrations are append-only** — add `supabase/migrations/YYYYMMDDHHMMSS_description.sql`; never edit migrations already applied
- **RLS-first** — frontend uses anon/publishable key; enforce product rules in policies and SECURITY DEFINER RPCs
- Name migrations: `YYYYMMDDHHMMSS_snake_case.sql` (match existing files)
- Reference domain behavior in migration comments; details in **`product-spec.md`**

## Key tables

`votes`, `vote_options`, `ballots`, `ballot_rankings` — see `20260421120000_ballotbox_core.sql`. RLS + helpers in `20260616120000_ballotbox_rls.sql`.

## Local

```bash
supabase db reset       # apply all migrations
supabase migration new <name>
```

After schema changes: update frontend types/queries if needed and run **`make check`**.
